_00184_003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190705%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190705-0705_00184_003.html&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=d70b1012\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190705/mobile/odn-20190705-0705_00184_003.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「閒時故把忠臣慢，差時不聽忠臣勸，危時卻要忠臣幹。」元代雜劇這段台詞正是香港真實寫照。愛國愛港人士過去長期受到港英政府打壓，有冤無路訴，以為回歸後可以揚眉吐氣，沒想到事與願違，不但依然得不到任何支持，有時候遭受的歧視更甚於回歸前，許多人心灰意冷，或淪為維園阿伯，或自動消失。在這種情況下，即使中央有意為香港撥亂反正，也未必可以找到可靠力量，也未必有人願意衝鋒陷陣。今次修例風波中，建制陣營不乏首鼠兩端之徒，港府高官更是紛紛龜縮，這已足以說明一切，寄望這種「牆頭草」治港，一國兩制不走樣變形才怪。幸好還有執法者這道最後防線，否則局面勢必更加混亂、更加不可收拾"},{"pid":"e9e6d96eee8cdecedfceb30e2db05dc5b11908a6","tid":1298314,"uid":59869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a44076a82721b78540447a6b23890fdacf81eb58","tid":1298314,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"呢篇係咪改文黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係<br />\n東方其實成日都鬧建制派牆邊草投機分子無撚用"},{"pid":"34d2264dbdd70abfdb8a455ca662e93e9646a7b0","tid":1298314,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ba305fd568ec0d66e5df11c9353d8655e4318d","tid":1298314,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tvs7H4rmhw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dtvs7H4rmhw8&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=74f90110\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tvs7H4rmhw8</a><br />\n6:35開始聽<br />\n<br />\n你就知點解民建聯唔代表中聯辦利益！"},{"pid":"6b8b92707c428c031f8f4f7370809f8b